.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 6. High Protein Egg and Quinoa Bowl\\n- **Ingredients:**\\n  - 1 cup cooked quinoa\\n  - 2 large eggs\\n  - 1/2 avocado, sliced\\n  - 1/4 cup black beans\\n  - 1/4 cup diced tomatoes\\n  - Salt and pepper to taste\\n  - Olive oil for cooking\\n- **Instructions:** \\n  Scramble eggs in olive oil, mix with quinoa, beans, and tomatoes, and top with avocado.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 7. High Protein Smoothie\\n- **Ingredients:**\\n  - 1 cup spinach\\n  - 1 banana\\n  - 1 cup Greek yogurt\\n  - 1 scoop protein powder\\n  - 1 tablespoon peanut butter\\n  - 1 cup almond milk\\n- **Instructions:** \\n  Blend all ingredients until smooth and enjoy.\\n\\n---\\n\\nLet me know if you need any further assistance!", "tool_calls": [], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "invalid_tool_calls": []}
