"1 teaspoon sugar\\",\\"1 cup unsalted butter, chilled and diced\\",\\"6 to 8 tablespoons ice water\\",\\"6 to 8 apples, peeled, cored, and sliced\\",\\"3/4 cup sugar\\",\\"2 tablespoons all-purpose flour\\",\\"1 teaspoon cinnamon\\",\\"1/4 teaspoon nutmeg\\",\\"1 tablespoon lemon juice\\",\\"1 tablespoon butter\\"],\\"instructions\\":[\\"Preheat oven to 425°F (220°C).\\",\\"In a bowl, combine flour, salt, and sugar.\\",\\"Cut in butter until mixture resembles coarse crumbs.\\",\\"Stir in ice water, a tablespoon at a time, until mixture forms a ball.\\",\\"Divide dough in half, shape into discs, wrap in plastic, and refrigerate for 4 hours or overnight.\\",\\"Roll out one disc to fit the pie pan and place in the pan.\\",\\"In a large bowl, toss sliced apples with sugar, flour, cinnamon, nutmeg, and lemon juice.\\",\\"Fill the pie crust with the apple mixture and dot with butter.\\",\\"Roll out the second disc, place over the filling, seal edges, and cut slits for ventilation.\\",\\"Bake in the preheated oven for 15 minutes, reduce temperature to 350°F (175°C), and continue baking for 35 to 45 minutes until apples are soft and crust is golden brown.\\"],\\"created_at\\":\\"2026-03-05T09:46:23.905806\\"},{\\"id\\":9,\\"title\\":\\"High Protein Cottage Cheese Bowl\\",\\"ingredients\\":[\\"1 cup cottage cheese\\",\\"1/2 cup sliced peaches\\",\\"1/4 cup walnuts\\",\\"1 tablespoon honey\\",\\"1 tablespoon cinnamon\\"],\\"instructions\\":[\\"In a bowl, scoop the cottage cheese.\\",\\"Top with sliced peaches, walnuts, honey, and sprinkle with cinnamon.\\",\\"Mix gently and enjoy.\\"],\\"created_at\\":\\"2026-03-05T09:20:10.830511\\"},{\\"id\\":6,\\"title\\":\\"High Protein Egg and Quinoa Bowl\\",\\"ingredients\\":[\\"1 cup cooked quinoa\\",\\"2 large eggs\\",\\"1/2 avocado, sliced\\",\\"1/4 cup black beans\\",\\"1/4 cup diced tomatoes\\",\\"Salt and pepper to taste\\",\\"Olive oil for cooking\\"],\\"instructions\\":[\\"Heat olive oil in a skillet over medium heat.\\",\\"Scramble the eggs until fully cooked.\\",\\"In a bowl, combine cooked quinoa, scrambled eggs, black beans, and diced tomatoes.\\",\\"Top with sliced avocado and season with salt and pepper.\\",\\"Serve warm.\\"],\\"created_at\\":\\"2026-03-04T15:42:23.870087\\"},{\\"id\\":5,\\"title\\":\\"High Protein Smoothie\\",\\"ingredients\\":[\\"1 cup spinach\\",\\"1 banana\\",\\"1 cup Greek yogurt\\",\\"1 scoop protein powder\\",\\"1 tablespoon peanut butter\\",\\"1 cup almond milk\\"],\\"instructions\\":[\\"Combine spinach, banana, Greek yogurt, protein powder, peanut butter, and almond milk in a blender.\\",\\"Blend until smooth.\\",\\"Pour into a glass and enjoy.\\"],\\"created_at\\":\\"2026-03-04T15:38:08.859035\\"}]", "tool_call_id": "call_xctt5ZOcnjgElb3zonQnbWDi", "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}}
